'''Roknia''' is a [[necropolis]] in the [[Guelma]] region of north-east [[Algeria]] consisting of more than 7000 [[dolmen]]s spread over an area of 2&nbsp;km.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.geneawiki.com/index.php/Alg%C3%A9rie_-_Roknia|title=Algérie - Roknia — GeneaWiki|website=www.geneawiki.com|language=fr|access-date=2018-02-01}}</ref>

